BORIVALI – NAIGAON UP & DOWN FAST LINES FROM 11:00 AM TO 3:00 PM 

CENTRAL LINE 
MATUNGA – MULUND DOWN FAST LINE FROM 10:15 AM TO 3:15 PM

CSMT – CHUNABHATTI / BANDRA DOWN LINE FROM 11:40 AM TO 4:40 PM &

-------------------------------------------- 
Details 

WESTERN LINE

BORIVALI – NAIGAON UP & DOWN FAST LINES FROM 11:00 AM TO 3:00 PM 
• During the block, all Up fast trains will run on Up slow line Ex Virar/Vasai Road to Borivali & all Down fast trains will run on Down slow line Ex Borivali to Vasai Road/Virar. 

CENTRAL LINE

MATUNGA – MULUND DOWN FAST LINE FROM 10:15 AM TO 3:15 PM 
• Down fast/semi fast services leaving CSMT from 9:38 am to 2:54 pm will be diverted on Down slow line between Matunga & Mulund stations halting at all stations between Sion & Mulund stations & will arrive destination 20 minutes behind schedule. Down Fast trains beyond Thane will be re-diverted on Down fast line from Mulund. 
• All Up fast/semi fast services leaving Thane from 10:46 am to 3:19 pm will halt at Mulund, Bhandup, Vikhroli, Ghatkopar & Kurla stations in addition to their respective scheduled halts & will arrive destination 15 minutes behind schedule. 
• All slow services arriving & leaving CSMT between 11:00 am & 5:00 pm will arrive destination 10 minutes behind schedule 
• All long distance trains leaving CSMT & Dadar during the block period will be diverted on Down slow line between Matunga & Mulund & will run 30 minutes behind schedule.   

HARBOUR LINE

CSMT – CHUNABHATTI / BANDRA DOWN LINE FROM 11:40 AM TO 4:40 PM & 
CHUNABHATTI / BANDRA - CSMT UP LINE FROM 11:10 AM TO 4:10 PM 
• Down Harbour line services to Vashi / Belapur /Panvel leaving CSMT/Vadala Road from 11:34 am to 4:47 pm & Down Harbour line services to Bandra/Andheri/Goregaon leaving CSMT from 9:56 am to 4:43 pm will remain suspended. 
• Up Harbour line services for CSMT leaving Panvel/Belapur/Vashi from 9:53 am to 3:20 pm & Up Harbour line services leaving Bandra/Andheri/Goregaon from 10:45 am to 4:58 pm will remain suspended. 
• However, Special services will run between Panvel & Kurla (Platform No.8) during the block period. 
• Harbour line passengers are permitted to travel via Main Line & Western Railway from 10.00 am to 6.00 pm during block period.

column8:
Megablock on 22 July 2018, Sunday


WESTERN LINE 
BORIVALI – NAIGAON UP & DOWN FAST LINES FROM 11:00 AM TO 3:00 PM 

CENTRAL LINE 
MATUNGA – MULUND DOWN FAST LINE FROM 10:15 AM TO 3:15 PM 

HARBOUR LINE 
CSMT – CHUNABHATTI / BANDRA DOWN LINE FROM 11:40 AM TO 4:40 PM & 
CHUNABHATTI / BANDRA - CSMT UP LINE FROM 11:10 AM TO 4:10 PM 

-------------------------------------------- 
Details 

WESTERN LINE

BORIVALI – NAIGAON UP & DOWN FAST LINES FROM 11:00 AM TO 3:00 PM 
• During the block, all Up fast trains will run on Up slow line Ex Virar/Vasai Road to Borivali & all Down fast trains will run on Down slow line Ex Borivali to Vasai Road/Virar. 

CENTRAL LINE

MATUNGA – MULUND DOWN FAST LINE FROM 10:15 AM TO 3:15 PM 
• Down fast/semi fast services leaving CSMT from 9:38 am to 2:54 pm will be diverted on Down slow line between Matunga & Mulund stations halting at all stations between Sion & Mulund stations & will arrive destination 20 minutes behind schedule. Down Fast trains beyond Thane will be re-diverted on Down fast line from Mulund. 
• All Up fast/semi fast services leaving Thane from 10:46 am to 3:19 pm will halt at Mulund, Bhandup, Vikhroli, Ghatkopar & Kurla stations in addition to their respective scheduled halts & will arrive destination 15 minutes behind schedule. 
• All slow services arriving & leaving CSMT between 11:00 am & 5:00 pm will arrive destination 10 minutes behind schedule 
• All long distance trains leaving CSMT & Dadar during the block period will be diverted on Down slow line between Matunga & Mulund & will run 30 minutes behind schedule.   

HARBOUR LINE

CSMT – CHUNABHATTI / BANDRA DOWN LINE FROM 11:40 AM TO 4:40 PM & 
CHUNABHATTI / BANDRA - CSMT UP LINE FROM 11:10 AM TO 4:10 PM 
• Down Harbour line services to Vashi / Belapur /Panvel leaving CSMT/Vadala Road from 11:34 am to 4:47 pm & Down Harbour line services to Bandra/Andheri/Goregaon leaving CSMT from 9:56 am to 4:43 pm will remain suspended. 
• Up Harbour line services for CSMT leaving Panvel/Belapur/Vashi from 9:53 am to 3:20 pm & Up Harbour line services leaving Bandra/Andheri/Goregaon from 10:45 am to 4:58 pm will remain suspended. 
• However, Special services will run between Panvel & Kurla (Platform No.8) during the block period. 
• Harbour line passengers are permitted to travel via Main Line & Western Railway from 10.00 am to 6.00 pm during block period.
